#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: src/commands/exportopenpgpcertstoservercommand.cpp:110
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Exporting the certificate to a key server is not possible because the usage "
"of key servers has been disabled explicitly."
msgid_plural ""
"Exporting the certificates to a key server is not possible because the usage "
"of key servers has been disabled explicitly."
msgstr[0] ""
"鍵サーバの用途として明示的に禁止されているので、その鍵サーバに証明書をエクス"
"ポートすることはできません。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: src/commands/exportopenpgpcertstoservercommand.cpp:125
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>When OpenPGP certificates have been exported to a public directory "
"server, it is nearly impossible to remove them again.</para><para>Before "
"exporting your certificate to a public directory server, make sure that you "
"have created a revocation certificate so you can revoke the certificate if "
"it is compromised, lost, or you forgot the passphrase.</para><para>Are you "
"sure you want to continue?</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>公共のディレクトリサーバに OpenPGP 証明書をエクスポートした場合、そこか"
"ら削除することはほぼ不可能です。</para><para>公共のディレクトリサーバにあなた"
"の証明書をエクスポートする前に、取消証明書を必ず作成してください。これで、も"
"し、証明書が侵害、紛失したり、パスフレーズを忘れた場合に、証明書を取消できま"
"す。</para><para>本当に操作を続けますか？</para>"

